{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo_tutorials/pullrequests/262/comments/9260119.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo_tutorials/pull-requests/262/_/diff#comment-9260119"}}, "parent": {"id": 9257130, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo_tutorials/pullrequests/262/comments/9257130.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo_tutorials/pull-requests/262/_/diff#comment-9257130"}}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 262, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo_tutorials/pullrequests/262.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo_tutorials/pull-requests/262"}}, "title": "animated_box: Update file links."}, "content": {"raw": "OK I did some digging. Two lines in CMakeLists.txt are necessary to make a build from the 4.0 branch work for me:\n\n\n```\n#!cmake\nfind_package(gazebo REQUIRED)\n\nset (CMAKE_CXX_FLAGS \"${CMAKE_CXX_FLAGS} ${GAZEBO_CXX_FLAGS}\")\n```\n\nThen I'm only left with a lot of deprecation warnings due to ignition e.g.\n> 'SetRotation' has been explicitly marked deprecated here", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>OK I did some digging. Two lines in CMakeLists.txt are necessary to make a build from the 4.0 branch work for me:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite language-cmake\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"nb\">find_package</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">gazebo</span> <span class=\"s\">REQUIRED</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"nb\">set</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">CMAKE_CXX_FLAGS</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;${CMAKE_CXX_FLAGS} ${GAZEBO_CXX_FLAGS}&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>Then I'm only left with a lot of deprecation warnings due to ignition e.g.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>'SetRotation' has been explicitly marked deprecated here</p>\n</blockquote>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2015-08-20T18:34:07.262089+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "p.gorczak@gmail.com", "uuid": "{8f8e0a43-bd